caption.text:
Bogor🐾Beijing

#throwback #latepost #explorebeijing #explorechina🇨🇳

Dear SASMITA CLAUDIA PONTOH 🤗
.
Thanks for one year unforgettable moments selama kita mengarungi kehidupan perantauan d China .. I'm glad to have you as my roommate ❤
.
Thanks for becoming more than just my partner in crime, but some of my biggest mood booster in every single day 🙌
.
Thanks for being my guardian 24/7, who always taking care of me, yg selalu dengerin segala macam curhatan penting dan ga penting--rayuan gombal--candaan lucu n garing--cerita coro yg ga abis2 , give many good advices--suggestions, AND (the most important) temen gosib sepanjang segala abad 🙈🙈
.
I'm so lucky because you always being there when I need someone to lean on and don't know where to go 🙏
.
From now , no one becoming my MUA that always checking my eyebrow---eyeliner everyday, who always asking "mon, does this shirt make me look fat?", or whimpering "mon, let's eat jimifan", who trying to kiss and hug me every night (and I also doing those 😜), who always making me a big bowl of samyang, who almost everytime come out with a new shopping bag when we're going inside mall , who love spicy too much (until I confused she bought a meal with spicy taste or bought chili with rice topping), who don't have any weird face expressions when eat something sour, who always getting hot and sweaty even when we walking outside in the WINTER season🙊🙊
.
From now maybe we have a different life but I always pray the best for your life .. don't forget our promises to travel around the world (Disneyland Hong Kong, Zhangjiajie, Menado, Bandung, and Tornado Dufan are our first list), always keep contact, always telling the truth, always telling our secret, becoming your bridesmaid, and I will be in your prewedding till honeymoon (?) with your future husband (I wish he isn't jimifan or bakso malang laoban 👅)
.
I love those pict above: our speciality photo expresions (duck face and tongue out), everytime I tried becoming your photobomb!
.
I'm not a perfect nor sweet friend till now but still I wanna becoming your long term life partner 🙆
.
I WILL MISS YOU SO DAMN MUCH !
LOVE YOU TO THE PLUTO AND NEVER EVER BACK 😘
DESPACITO 🤘
.
.
xoxo,
Monika Velica 林莫兰💋
Upin to ipin
Hongkong, 13 Juli 2017
